				<p>

					To do that, you need to think of all the possible questions your guests are going to have and try to answer them in the content of your invitation.

				</p>
				<p>
					You're also going to need to figure out what information you're going to need back from them to help you plan your wedding, such as simple RSVPs for guest numbers and things like menu choices.

